# Git commits

- All commit messages (subject + optional body) must be written in **English**.
- Prefer imperative, clear subjects (e.g. `feat:`, `fix:`, `docs:`).

## Dual remote (required when publishing)

This repo is expected to have **two remotes**:

1. `git push forgejo <branch>`
2. `git push origin <branch>`

Do not consider work “published” until both pushes succeed, unless explicitly instructed otherwise.

